flow_desc: To add Google Pay as a payment option, the user starts by tapping the profile icon in the DoorDash app to access their account settings. They then navigate to the "Payment Methods" section, where they can see their saved payment options. Next, they tap on the Google Pay icon to add it as a new payment method. The user is guided through the steps, assisting them in completing the integration of Google Pay into their account efficiently. This flow ensures a smooth user experience, enabling easier transactions for future orders on the platform.
